OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers will continue across the north
OL,7,Fthrough this evening and overnight. It
OL,8,Fwill be dry elsewhere with clear
OL,9,Fperiods. Frost developing under
OL,10,Flengthy cloud breaks.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA mainly dry and chilly start.
OL,13,FThickening cloud and rain will spread
OL,14,Fto the north by late morning and
OL,15,Felsewhere during the afternoon.
OL,16,FTurning drier through the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
